snippet.title: Exclusive Beyond Divinity  trailer by GOG.com
snippet.description:
This is an exclusive GOG.com trailer video for Beyond Divinity .

You can buy this game on GOG.com for $9.99,
visit http://www.gog.com/en/gamecard/beyond_divinity for more information.
